        <section>
            <page_title>
                <title>Welcome in a world of treasures and... mechanics</title>
            </page_title>
            <p>You can not build standard wooden tools in this modpack!</p>
            <p>So in order to get going you need to find a few things</p>
            <p>oh and make sure to get it fast because you will die to thirst or hunger!</p>
            <link indent="8" ref="START:hurryup">So HURRY UP!</link>
        </section>
    </chapter>
    <chapter id="START">
        <section id="hurryup">
            <page_title>
                <title>2. Hurry up or die!</title>
            </page_title>
            <p>You need flint, which comes out of gravel or by breaking pebbles on each other.</p>
            <p>You need sticks which will be dropped from leaves or can be found on the ground</p>
            <p>Go and find at least 6 flint and 4 sticks!</p>
        </section>
